subject: Football
lead_paragraph: Nate Kaeding kicked a 21-yard field goal as time expired in the A.F.C.’s 31-28 victory against the N.F.C. on Saturday. N.F.C. quarterback Drew Brees dislocated his left elbow, but it is unlikely to affect him next season.
